data.description: Very Desirable, Cabin on 20 ac. of breathtaking meadow views with Creek meandering through. Build a greenhouse, plant a garden next to the 12 apple and pear trees. Also, has a chicken Coop w/ automatic heat and water heater.  Shop with work bench area, and shed is stuffed with wood. Artesian Well has water pressure even if power goes out. 2, 500 gal propane tanks w/last 2 years. Property is located at the end of a private drive, and is only 3 miles from Elk City.  Plenty of Elk, Deer, and Turkeys to appreciate. This area offers hundreds of miles of groomed snowmobile and ATV trails. This is a perfect recreational get-away that sleeps 10. Home features a huge loft that can be used as a 3rd bedroom/recreation room, also plumbed for a 2nd bathroom. Also has 11' ceilings. Generator connection, RV electrical Hook-up. Also, has Elon Musk Starlink Satellite System, and SimpliSafe security system which transfer at closing. K-8th grade school in Elk City. 26 tons of new rock added to Driveway.
